39:45.883 --> 39:47.752 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
get fined?

39:47.752 --> 39:50.922 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN:
What's the fine?

39:50.922 --> 39:52.690 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL SORRELL: So, there's
