prayer squats or pay $200.

39:58.263 --> 40:02.934 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Four hundred
prayer squats for being out of
dress code?

40:02.934 --> 40:06.104 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL SORRELL: It's better
