40:54.252 --> 40:57.822 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
STUDENT: This is where all
your classes will be held.

40:57.822 --> 40:59.724 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Freshman
Jennifer Moreno is a
first-generation student whose
parents

40:59.724 --> 41:01.659 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
