career aspirations.

41:27.652 --> 41:32.623 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Senior Destiny
Modeste is interning at
Slingshot, an advertising agency

41:32.623 --> 41:35.493 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
