42:00.051 --> 42:05.056 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
This is an investment in
improving the talent pool of
your company and your office.

42:05.056 --> 42:07.492 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So what's the
incentive for an employer to
keep that student around?

42:07.492 --> 42:11.396 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL SORRELL: Well, don't
keep them around if they aren't
good enough, right?

42:11.396 --> 42:15.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Our responsibility to them is
provide a quality product.

42:15.900 --> 42:20.471 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Chris
Hawthorne, who runs the intern
program at Slingshot, says the

42:20.471 --> 42:24.175 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
partnership with an historically
black college is important.

42:24.175 --> 42:26.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS HAWTHORNE, Slingshot: We
have, as an industry, in
advertising, struggled with
attracting

42:26.978 --> 42:29.313 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
