field of advertising.

42:29.313 --> 42:32.216 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So we started this
relationship with Paul Quinn.

42:32.216 --> 42:35.052 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We met Destiny, and
she was fantastic.

42:35.052 --> 42:39.223 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But as
important as career and college
are to Sorrell's vision, he also

42:39.223 --> 42:42.560 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
pushes his students to
engage in community service.

42:42.560 --> 42:47.031 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL SORRELL: We believe that
colleges have a fundamental
responsibility, if you're

42:47.031 --> 42:50.101 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
