43:10.621 --> 43:14.091 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL SORRELL: Someone's going
to figure out the urban issues.

43:14.091 --> 43:16.861 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Why shouldn't it be the people
who came from those urban
communities that have a vested

43:16.861 --> 43:20.465 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
