43:20.465 --> 43:23.501 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In keeping
with that mission, the college
donates 10 percent of the
produce

43:23.501 --> 43:27.905 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from the farm, named WE over Me,
to the surrounding underserved
community.

43:27.905 --> 43:31.309 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VINCENT OWOSENI: If you look at
the need around you, and you
look at your resource, you can,

43:31.309 --> 43:37.215 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
say, hey, I can use this space
right here to grow what my
community needs.

43:37.215 --> 43:40.618 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Where someone else sees
hopelessness, you see an
opportunity.

43:40.618 --> 43:43.788 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In Dallas, for
the "PBS NewsHour," I'm Hari
Sreenivasan.

43:43.788 --> 43:48.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And, tomorrow,
