Report explore why.

44:05.243 --> 44:10.081 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Finally tonight,
we return to our coverage of the
15th anniversary of

44:10.081 --> 44:14.151 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the September 11 attacks
and the aftermath.

44:14.151 --> 44:20.424 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A decade-and-a-half after the
U.S. invasion, Afghanistan is
still rebuilding and heavily

44:20.424 --> 44:24.595 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
dependent on international aid,
relying on other countries for
70 percent of its government

44:24.595 --> 44:26.564 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
